long_description: in 1959, owens liquors began as a small family owned and operated store in myrtle beach, sc. creating another updated state of the art shopping experience for our retail and wholesale customers. owens liquors is conveniently located on north kings hwy (17 business) between 79th and 82nd ave north, in myrtle beach. our site lists those states where common carriers will deliver alcohol. the company does not sell alcohol to persons under the age of 21. the company makes every effort to ensure that alcoholic beverages are not delivered to anyone who is under the age of 21. by arranging for transportation of the alcoholic beverages, owens liquors is providing a service to, and acting on behalf of you. this also includes providing legal proof that you are over 21 year of age (california, or other acceptable state's driver's license or passport). a wine and liquor (spirits) store located in 8000 n kings hwy, myrtle beach, sc 29572, usa.
